                    <div class="columns eight banner-text">
                        <p class="intro-text">President Obama said if Congress won&#8217;t act on the issue, &#8220;I will.&#8221; Say you will support President Obama&#8217;s plan and take action in your own community now.</p>
                        <h1><img src="https://secure.assets.bostatic.com/frontend/projects/i-will/img/logo.png" alt="I will help President Obama and take action to combat climate change."></h1>
                        <form id="" method="POST" action="https://my.barackobama.com/page/signup/i-will-hero" class="inline">
                            <ol>
                                <li class="email"><label for="hero_email">Email</label><input type="email" name="email" value="" id="hero_email" required placeholder="Email"></li>
                                <li class="zip"><label for="hero_zip">ZIP Code</label><input type="text" name="zip" value="" id="hero_zip" required pattern="[\d]{5}(-[\d]{4})?" placeholder="ZIP"></li>
                                <li class="button"><button type="submit" class="">I'm in</button></li>
                            </ol>
                            <input type="hidden" name="bp_load_counter" value="1">
                            <input name="redirect_url" type="hidden" value="">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
